[[module CSS]]
#page-title {
  display: none;
}

.meta-title {
  border-bottom: solid 1px #bbbbbb;
  color: #990011;
  font-weight: normal;
  margin: 0 0 0.6em;
  padding: 0 0 0.25em;
  font-size: 200%;
}

.meta-title p {
  margin: 0;
}



.page-source::before{
content: '项目编号：待分配 \A\A
项目等级：Keter（更新：Decommissioned）\A\A
特殊收容措施：更新：重写画卷 \A\A
